    <text>
        <body>
            <div style="handwritten" type="letter" xml:id="d.1">
                <head type="title">Miklós Oláh to Kristóf Batthyány (Vienna, 21 August
                    [1552])</head>
                <floatingText type="regesta">
                    <body>
                        <p xml:id="reg.p.1">He understands what Kristóf Batthyány wrote, and he has
                            sent the prepared letter to the King. He has spoken about the other
                            cases with Ferenc Batthyány, who said he would make sure the estates are
                            prised from Pálffy’s hands. Until then Ferenc Batthyány will cover the
                            income those estates would yield that year.</p>
                    </body>
                </floatingText>
                <pb/>
                <p xml:id="p.1">Magnifice Domine et Amice nobis Honorande, salutem!</p>
                <p xml:id="p.2">Ea, de quibus Dominatio Vestra nobis scripsit, intelleximus,
                    litteras regiae maiestatis pro Dominatione Vestra necessarias expeditas ad eam
                    misimus. De aliis rebus locuti fuimus nuper cum domino <persName>Francisco
                        Bathyany</persName>,<note xml:id="note.1">Ferenc Batthyány.</note> qui
                    respondit se curaturum esse, ut bona de manu <persName>Laurentii litterati
                        Palffy</persName><note xml:id="note.2">Lőrinc Pálffy († after 1557), often
                        called <hi rend="italic">litteratus</hi>, a prosecutor and a magistrate of
                        the Royal Court, see <hi rend="smallcap">Nagy</hi> 1862, 39.</note>
                    liberentur. Quae etiam in praesentia liberari non possunt, se tamen daturum esse
                    Dominationi Vestrae tantum, quantum proventus bonorum illorum hoc anno facerent.
                    Dominationem Vestra bene valere optamus.</p>
                <p xml:id="p.3">Datum <placeName>Viennae</placeName> 21. Augusti.</p>
                <p xml:id="p.4">
                    <seg type="signature">
                        <add corresp="Olahus" type="insert">Vester Agriensis etc. propria manu</add>
                    </seg>
                </p>
                <pb/>
            </div>
            <div style="handwritten" type="verso" xml:id="d.2">
                <head>On the outer side:</head>
                <p xml:id="p.5"> Magnifico domino Christophoro de Bathyan, magistro pincernarum
                    regiae maiestatis etc. domino et amico nobis honorandissimo.</p>
            </div>
        </body>
